my best friend 's wedding is a 1997 american romantic comedy film directed by p.j. hogan , starring julia roberts . the film received generally positive reviews from critics and was a global box-office hit . it is considered as one of the best and classic romantic comedy films of all time . the soundtrack song " i say a little prayer ( for you ) " was covered by singer diana king and featured heavily in the film , making it a billboard top 100 hit . the soundtrack featured a number of burt &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; david songs . a chinese remake of the same name was released in china on 5 august 2016 .